        <actionDate>2026-05-11</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2026-06-12T19:32:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Innovative Maternal Payment and Coverage To Save Moms Act or the IMPACT to Save Moms Act</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services to establish the Perinatal Care Alternative Payment Model Demonstration Project through FY2031 to allow states to test payment models for maternity care, including postpartum care, under Medicaid and the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP).&nbsp;</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
